  <thing id="fResAcidSp" name="Acid Splatter" description="You can channel magical energy into orbs of acid.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 2nd-level spells.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have an acid spell of 2nd level or higher available to cast, you can throw an orb of acid as a ranged touch attack. The attack has a range of 5 feet per level of the highest-level acid spell you have available to cast and deals 1d6 points of damage per level of that acid spell.\n\nAs a secondary benefit, you gain a +1 competence bonus to your caster level when casting acid spells.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Mage" compset="Feat" summary="Acid spell 2nd+, ranged touch up to 5 ft &amp; 1d6 acid dam per spl lvl." uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Pre req (Done)

Reserve feats are wizard bonus feats. (Done)

Reserve feats are Su abilities, need to make specials. (Done)

Reserve specials should be unique and count feats that add them, making the summ adjust. (Done)</comment>
    <usesource source="CompMage"/>
    <tag group="SpecType" tag="Attack"/>
    <tag group="fCategory" tag="Reserve"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="ShowSpec"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Super"/>
