  <thing id="fStormBolt" name="Storm Bolt" description="The electrical energy contained within your magic rages inside you, begging to be released.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 3rd level spells.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have an electricity spell of 3rd level or higher available to cast, you can fire a 20-foot line of electricity as a standard action. This bolt deals 1d6 points of electricity damage per level of the highest-level electricity spell you have available to cast. A successful Reflex save halves damage.\n\nAs a secondary benefit, you gain a +1 competence bonus to your caster level when casting electricity spells.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Mage" compset="Feat" summary="Elec spl 3rd+, stand, 20 ft line does 1d6 x spl lvl electricity dam (Ref half)." uniqueness="useronce">
