  <thing id="fVenSpirit" name="Vengeful Spirit" description="Your watchful spirit takes revenge on foes that have harmed you.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Watchful spirit class feature (see the wu jen class in Complete Arcane).\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: If you use an initiative reroll from your watchful spirit class feature, the first creature to deal damage to you in the encounter immediately takes half the damage it dealt to you. This damage is untyped, so damage reduction and resistance or immunity does not apply.\n\nAlso, you gain one extra initiative reroll from your watchful spirit class feature.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Mage" compset="Feat" summary="When use watchful spirit reroll, 1st foe to dam you takes &#189; untyped dam." uniqueness="useronce">
