  <thing id="fWinterBla" name="Winter&apos;s Blast" description="The frozen magic within you can burst forth in a hail of frost.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to cast 2nd-level spells.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: As long as you have a cold spell of 2nd level or higher available to cast, you can create a 15-foot cone-shaped burst of cold. This cone deals 1d4 points of cold damage per level of the highest-level cold spell you have available to cast. A successful Reflex save halves the damage.\n\nAs a secondary benefit, you gain a +1 competence bonus to your caster level when casting cold spells.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Mage" compset="Feat" summary="Cold spl 2nd+, stand, 1d4 x spl lvl dam in 15 ft cone (Ref half)." uniqueness="useronce">
