  <thing id="sDrdBlaRot" name="Blackrot" description="{i}The plant-matter creaks and writhes beneath your hand as you generate a malignant rot at its center.{/i}\n\nThis spell allows you to deliver a single touch that either damages a plant creature over a number of rounds or renders a wooden weapon poisonous.\n\nWhen used as a touch attack against a plant creature, the spell deals ld8 points of damage per round. A successful Fortitude save reduces the duration to 1 round.\n\nAlternatively, you can touch a weapon with a wooden striking surface (such as a club or quarterstaff). Any creature damaged by the weapon is sickened for 1 round unless it succeeds on a Fortitude save. Treat this as a poison effect for creatures immune or resistant to such effects." compset="Spell" summary="Deal damage to plant creatures, or use wooden weapon to sicken foes.">
