  <thing id="sSpTPalTwi" name="Pall of Twilight" description="{i}A creeping pall of darkness covers the area like running ink, muting sound and color alike.{/i}\n\nThis spell reduces illumination in the area to shadowy; these shadows are mental as well as physical. All creatures in the area take a -10 penalty on Listen, Search, Sense Motive, and Spot\nchecks. A successful Will save negates these penalties, but not the effect of the darkness." compset="Spell" summary="Veil of shadow impedes sight and sound.">
