  <thing id="sSpTAIcyHu" name="Aspect of the Icy Hunter" description="{i}Thick ivory fur grows from your skin and your back hunches over until you stand on four paws. Cold, blue eyes stare out of your now-canine face.{/i}\n\nYou take the form of a winter wolf (MM 256). You gain 20 temporary hit points, which disappear at the end of the spell&apos;s duration. See the Polymorph Subschool sidebar on page 91 for more details." compset="Spell" summary="You take the form of a winter wolf.">
