  <thing id="sHexFinAgo" name="Finger of Agony" description="{i}As you crook your finger, your enemy feels his vitals rupture within him.{/i}\n\nYou magically disrupt the subject&apos;s internal organs, causing it great pain. Each round on your turn, the subject takes 3d6 points of damage and becomes nauseated for 1 round. A successful Fortitude save halves the damage and lessens the nauseated condition to sickened." compset="Spell" summary="Deals 3d6 damage per round and nauseates or sickens target.">
