  <thing id="sHexKarRet" name="Karmic Retribution" description="{i}By manipulating fate itself, you ensure that any who attack you suffer greatly for their insolence.{/i}\n\nThis spell functions like {i}karmic aura{/i}, except that any creature that damages you and fails its Will save becomes stunned for 1 round." compset="Spell" summary="Any creature damaging you becomes stunned for 1 round.">
