  <thing id="sHexDeaCal" name="Death&apos;s Call" description="{i}You release a scream that chills the air with deathly energy.{/i}\n\nAll living creatures within the area (other than you) take 1 point of damage per caster level (maximum 5) and become fatigued. A successful Fortitude save negates the fatigue.\nAny swarm in the area of death&apos;s call instead takes ld4 points of damage per caster level (maximum 5d4) and becomes fatigued (Fortitude save negates fatigue). This supersedes the normal +50% damage dealt to a swarm by an area spell." compset="Spell" summary="Scream deals 1 point of damage/level (more to swarms), fatigues all within 10 feet.">
