  <thing id="sBrdCacAla" name="Cacophonous Alarm" description="{i}Your magic causes the surrounding region to vibrate briefly with a deep rumble.{/i}\n\nThis spell functions like {i}alarm{/i}, although you can only set it to produce an audible result, not a mental one.\n\nFurthermore, an effect equivalent to a {i}sound burst{/i} spell affects the first creature to violate the warded area (only this creature is affected, not a 10-footradius spread)." compset="Spell" summary="First creature to trigger {i}alarm{/i} affected by {i}sound burst{/i} spell.">
