  <thing id="sBrdMasIde" name="Mask of the Ideal" description="{i}Your voice and features become more refined and pleasing.{/i}\n\n{i}Mask of the ideal{/i} shifts everything toward an ideal form. Any creature that perceives you in any fashion beholds something that it finds aesthetically pleasing.\n\nYou gain a +4 competence bonus on Bluff and Diplomacy checks, as well as on Disguise checks made to disguise yourself (but not others). You also gain a +4 competence bonus on any Charisma check you make to influence a creature that you have enchanted (such as with {i}charm person{/i}) or conjured (such as with {i}planar binding{/i})." compset="Spell" summary="Gain +4 bonus on skill checks, checks to influence enchanted or conjured creatures.">
