  <thing id="sBrdResThu" name="Resonating Thunder" description="{i}Waves of sound crash continuously upon the ears of those in the area.{/i}\n\nYou fill the area with discordant crashes of sonic energy that deal 4d6 points of sonic damage per round to creatures within the area. Furthermore, any creature within or entering the area becomes deafened as long as it remains within and for 1 round thereafter. A successful Fortitude save halves the damage and negates the deafened effect.\n\nThe clamorous sound in the area also interferes with all sonic spells and effects. Any such spell or effect has only a 50% chance to affect a creature within the area of {i}resounding thunder{/i}." compset="Spell" summary="Lasting sound deals 4d6 sonic damage per round, deafens creatures within area.">
