  <thing id="sDrdCliTre" name="Climbing Tree" description="{i}At your call, a tree snakes up from the earth, in seconds growing as tall as trees that have lived for years.{/i}\n\nYou cause a 1-foot-diameter tree to grow in the center of any adjacent square. The tree can grow as high as 10 feet per caster level (to a maximum of 50 feet). The branches are evenly spaced and perfect for climbing; ascending the tree requires a successful DC 5 Climb check.\n\nThe tree can grow only in soft terrain, such as dirt, soil, or sand. The tree has hardness 5 and 120 hit points; if cut down, it vanishes instantly. It can&apos;t be animated by any means, such as with {i}animate plants{/i}, nor can it serve as the basis for any plant-related spell such as {i}tree stride{/i}. Treat the tree as a slender pillar (DMG 64) for terrain purposes." compset="Spell" summary="Temporarily grow a tall tree for use as a ladder.">
