  <thing id="sDrdUniBlo" name="Unicorn Blood" description="{i}The power and purity of the unicorn surge through your veins.{/i}\n\nWhile this spell lasts, you gain immunity to poison and to compulsion and charm spells or effects.\n\nOnce while the spell lasts, you can use a swift action to bestow temporary hit points equal to your caster level (maximum 15) to another willing creature you touch. This ends the duration of {i}unicorn blood{/i} on you, though the temporary hit points last for the remainder of the original duration of the spell. You can&apos;t use this ability on yourself.\n\nIf you are under the effect of this spell and the {i}unicorn horn{/i} spell at the same time, you instead bestow temporary hit points equal to twice your caster level (maximum 30)." compset="Spell" summary="Gain immunity to poison, compulsion, charm effects; bestow temporary hp once.">
