  <thing id="sSorDrFoET" name="Dreaded Form of the Eye Tyrant" description="{i}Your body withers away to dust, leaving only a floating head, which quickly grows oversized and misshapen. Your eyes fuse together as a single orb in your forehead, and ten writhing eyestalks sprout from your skull.{/i}\n\nYou take the form of a beholder (MM 26). You gain 30 temporary hit points, which disappear at the end of the spell&apos;s duration. You can use only one eye ray each round, and each of your ten eye rays can be used only once during the spell&apos;s duration. For example, once you use your {i}disintegrate{/i} eye ray, you can&apos;t use that eye ray again during this casting of the spell. See the Polymorph Subschool sidebar on page 91 for more details." compset="Spell" summary="You take the form of a beholder.">
