  <thing id="cWrlAllSee" name="All-Seeing Eye (Least; 2nd)" description="You gain a supernaturally precise vision of the world around you. You gain the benefits of {i}comprehend languages{/i}, albeit for written words only. Additionally, you gain a +6 bonus on Search and Spot checks. {i}All-seeing eyes{/i} lasts for 24 hours." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
