  <thing id="cEDDamRed" name="Damage Reduction" description="You gain temporary damage reduction (overcome by cold iron) equal to 1/2 your class level (minimum 1).This damage reduction stacks with the damage reduction granted by the warlock class. This effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to 3 + your Cha modifier (minimum 1 round)." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
