  <thing id="cEDStrWil" name="Strength of Will" description="You gain a bonus equal to 1/2 your class level (minimum +1) on your next save to resist a mind-affecting spell or ability. This effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to 3 + your Cha modifier (minimum 1 round); if you haven&apos;t attempted an appropriate save in this time, the effect ends." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You gain a bonus to save against a mind-affecting spell or ability." uniqueness="useronce">
