  <thing id="cETGreBla" name="Greatreach Blast" description="This invocation (Greater; 5th; Eldritch Essence) allows you to place an arcane spell with a range of touch upon your {i}eldritch blast{/i}. If the {i}eldritch blast{/i} hits its target, the spell takes effect on that target as if you had touched it. If the {i}eldritch blast{/i} misses its target, the spell is lost with no effect.\n\nIt takes a full-round action to cast the spell and fire the {i}eldritch blast{/i}. Only a touch spell with a casting time no greater than 1 standard action can be placed upon your {i}eldritch blast{/i}.\n\nOnly the first target of your {i}eldritch blast{/i} is affected by the spell (for example, an {i}eldritch greatreach chain{/i} delivers the touch spell on the initial target, not on any of the secondary targets). If your {i}eldritch blast{/i} doesn&apos;t specify a target, you can&apos;t apply this invocation to the blast.\n\nTreat {i}greatreach blast{/i} as a spell whose level is equal to the touch spell placed upon the eldritch blast (minimum 5th level)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Place touch spells upon your {i}Eldritch Blast{/i}.">
